"2050500266" and "Rev:1.0" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. :This is the same text as is on the board of the [[SMC SMCWBR14-N5 rev A2]]. The RAM may be the 32MB A3S56D40FTP-G5.
Default settings are per the FCC sample label and manual. :The default SSID pattern is stated as '''Legrand_XXXXXX''', where '''XXXXXX''' is the last 6 digits of the MAC address.
The OUI (6C:FD:B9) ''may'' not be accurate.
